memberdef.name: psds

para.verbatim:
Plot Power Spectral Densities (PSDs) for multiple detectors in Tkinter.
Parameters: - event_name: Name of the gravitational wave event - detectors: List of detector names (e.g., ['H1', 'L1', 'V1']) - gps_start: GPS start time - gps_end: GPS end time - fftlengths: List of FFT lengths (same length as detectors) - methods: List of ASD computation methods (same length as detectors)
